          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">In UK, the default </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Decimal Symbol</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is a &apos;.&apos; (Stop, or Period(USA))</text></para>
